# Backend Core

This is the backend core project built with FastAPI.

## Setup

1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   uv sync
   # or
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

2. Run the server:
   ```bash
   uvicorn app.main:app --reload
   ```

See `.agent/rules/instructions.md` for development guidelines.
